                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/876" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0082</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9247 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">怎样才能让员工跟上公司战略转型的步伐？----基于华恒矿业有限公司的经验</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to let employees keep up with the pace of the company strategic transformation?----- Based on th</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵航</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东华恒矿业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织惯例；战略变革；国有企业；2012百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">organizational routines; strategic transformation; state-owned enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华恒矿业公司是一家典型的传统煤炭企业，在破产重组之后，脱掉了包袱，注入了优质资产，获得了新的发展机遇，确定了新的发展战略。战略转型对应了管理模式的转变，进而要求员工在思想观念和行为模式也应做出相应的转变，否则，新战略只能成为空想，而无法实现。但是，一个有着几十年历史的老国有企业，从上到下早已形成了一套牢固的组织“惯例”， “等靠要”情况很严重，缺乏竞争意识，而且，煤炭产业工人整体受教育水平较低，接受新鲜事物的能力偏低，制约了战略转型的效率。因此，如何改变员工的思维方式和行为方式，成为华恒矿业战略推进过程中首先要面对的巨大挑战，也是决定华恒矿业能否培育新型能力，全面落实新战略的关键。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Huaheng mining company is a typical traditional coal enterprise. After bankruptcy reorganization, Huaheng took off the baggage and injected the high quality assets. So Huaheng has a new development opportunities and identify new development strategy. Strategic transformation correspond to management model transformation, and then ask staff in the thought idea and behavior patterns also should make corresponding change, otherwise the new strategy can only be idealistic, and cannot be achieved. But A state-owned enterprise with decades of history had formed a strong organization routines . Employees have serious &quot;wait, lean, want&quot; thought and lack of competition consciousness. The coal industry workers affected by the low level of education. They have lower ability to accept new things. These problems restricted the strategic transformation efficiency. Therefore, the problem how to change the staff of the mode of thinking and behavior way are the first to be faced with huge challenge in Huaheng mining strategy of the process. For Huaheng mining company, the problem is the key to cultivate the new ability and implement a new strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《组织行为》、《组织变革与创新》、《企业文化》、《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业员工思想意识和行为习惯的转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-09</td>
                            </tr>
